{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_02_03",
  "title": "川咲さくら 3話 支えてくれるみんなへ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "思い出話を聞いていて思ったんですが\n麻奈さんって無邪気な人だったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hearing your stories got me thinking‚\nMana-san was a very innocent person‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "無邪気と言うか子供っぽいと言うか……\nそういう所も麻奈の魅力だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You could say innocent‚ or maybe childlike…\nThat side was part of Mana’s appeal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.666666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 14.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "さて、そろそろリハーサルが始まる時間だ\n麻奈の思い出話の続きはまた今度にしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ it’s about time for your rehearsal.\nWe can carry on with memories of Mana next time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 23.466666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんとの思い出を沢山聞かせてくれて\nありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for telling me so many of your\nmemories of Mana-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "どれも聞いてるだけで元気になるような\n素敵なお話でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They were all wonderful stories that\nliven me up‚ just listening to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても麻奈の話を聞きたいなんて\nどうして急にそんなことを言い出したんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But what put you in such a hurry to\nask to hear Mana stories now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a good one—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 42.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが今日のライブに大きな期待をしていることは\n前にも話しましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I mentioned before that everyone has\nhigh expectations for today’s show‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんを超える伝説のライブに\nなるんじゃないかとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re saying this might be a legendary show\nto surpass even Mana-san’s…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 54.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなみんなの期待に私はちゃんと応えられるのか\nずっと不安で仕方なかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve just been so worried for a long time about\nwhether I could live up to everyone’s expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 62.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "こんなもやもやした気持ちのままステージに立っても\nみんなをがっかりさせるんじゃないかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I get up on stage when I’m so unsure of myself‚\nI will let everyone down for sure…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 70.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことを考えながら歩いてたから\nうっかり事故を起こしそうになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what I was thinking about while I was walking‚\nand almost got into an accident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺がさくらの不安を払拭しないといけなかったのに\n何もしてやれなくてすまなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should have done something to take your worries away.\nI’m sorry I didn’t do anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 82.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、さっき{user}さんは\n私のことを本気で心配して怒ってくれましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But earlier‚ you were really upset because\nyou were truly concerned about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 92.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "その時に気付いたんです\n私のことを本気で想ってくれている人達がいるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s when I realized it.\nThere are people who really care about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 97.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんや星見プロの仲間達\nライブのスタッフさんにファンのみんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You‚ the people at Hoshimi Productions‚\nthe live show crew‚ and all the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 104.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "支えてくれるみんながいれば\n私はいくらでも頑張れるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If there are so many people supporting me‚\nI can try however hard it takes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 111.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私の体を支えてくれている麻奈さんからも\n勇気をもらえたらって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I thought‚ I wanted to gain some courage from Mana-san‚\nwho also lent support for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それで麻奈の話を聞きたがったのか……\n今日のライブは思い切り歌えそうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s why you wanted to hear about Mana…\nSo are you ready to sing your heart out for today’s show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 126.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　麻奈さんからいっぱい勇気をもらったので\nもう大丈夫です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I got so much courage from Mana-san‚\nso it’s going to be fine!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 131.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "見ていて下さい、麻奈さんに負けないくらい\n盛り上がるライブにしてみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just watch‚ and I’ll show you a performance\nexciting enough to keep up with Mana-san’s.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3466.666666666669,
          "startTime": 138.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "今日はライブに来てくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you all for coming to the show today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "みんなも知ってると思うけど\nこの会場は長瀬麻奈さんにゆかりのある場所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you all know this‚ but\nthis venue has a connection with Mana Nagase-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "私は麻奈さんと縁があって、そのせいで\nいろいろと比べられて期待されることも多くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ too‚ have a connection with Mana-san‚ and that makes people\ncompare us and have a lot of expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "だから今日このステージに立つことに\nプレッシャーを感じてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I was feeling a lot of pressure about\ngetting up on this stage today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr022.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんとみんなの期待に応えられるのか不安で\nいろいろ悩んだりしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was anxious about whether I could live up to your expectations‚\nand I had a lot on my mind‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr023.m4a",
      "text": "自分のことを思い直すきっかけがあって\n私は沢山の人に支えられてるんだって気付きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but something happened that made me think about myself anew.\nI realized I had so many people supporting me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr024.m4a",
      "text": "今日のライブもこんなに綺麗な演出をしてくれて\n私達のために大勢の人が力を尽くしてくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For today’s concert‚ we’ve got so many people doing their best\nto help us to put on a beautiful show‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr025.m4a",
      "text": "応援してくれるファンのみんな……\n星見プロの仲間達。スタッフやマネージャー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and all you fans rooting for us…\nand the people at Hoshimi Productions. The staff and our manager…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr026.m4a",
      "text": "そして、尊敬する先輩アイドルの麻奈さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Mana-san‚ our revered senpai idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr027.m4a",
      "text": "私はいつもみんなから光をもらっています\nみんながいるから私はアイドルとして輝けるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of you are shining your light on me all the time‚\nand I can shine as an idol because all of you are here for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr028.m4a",
      "text": "私がいつも元気でいられるのはみんなのおかげです\nだから今度は私の歌でみんなに元気を届けます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s thanks to you that I can always stay lively.\nSo this time around‚ I’m going to liven you all up with my singing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_03-skr029.m4a",
      "text": "これからも私達は輝き続けます\n私の歌があなたの光になれるように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re going to keep on shining.\nSo our songs can become your light.",
